videos.description: Quarterback Trace McSorley connects with a diving DeAndre Thompkins to put Penn State up 7-0.
videos.headline: McSorley gets PSU on board early with 40-yard TD pass

videos.description: Kent State's Woody Barrett connects with Mike Carrigan for a 47-yard touchdown to tie Penn State at 7-7.
videos.headline: Kent State strikes back with 47-yard TD

videos.description: Kent State attempts an onside kick after their touchdown to regain possession.
videos.headline: Kent State recovers onside kick

videos.description: Trace McSorley keeps it himself and runs in for touchdown to give Penn State a lead over Kent State.
videos.headline: McSorley sneaks in for PSU TD

videos.description: Trace McSorley pulls off another QB sneak into the end zone for his second rushing score of the day.
videos.headline: McSorley sneaks in again for another TD

videos.description: Trace McSorley is picked off by Kent State's Elvis Hines after a juggled pass.
videos.headline: Kent State's Hines makes great INT on McSorley

videos.description: Trace McSorley rushes 13 yards for his third running touchdown of the game to put Penn State up 28-10 at the half.
videos.headline: McSorley scores 3rd rushing TD of game

videos.description: Mark Allen muscles his way seven yards through the Kent State defense and dives to get the touchdown for Penn State.
videos.headline: Penn State's Allen runs 7 yards for TD

videos.description: Ricky Slade runs two yards for the touchdown on his first carry of the game to put Penn State up 42-10.
videos.headline: Penn State's Slade runs 2 yards for TD

videos.description: Trace McSorley throws a 41-yard touchdown pass to Brandon Polk for his fifth total touchdown of the game, tying a career high for McSorley.
videos.headline: McSorley ties career high with 5th total TD

videos.description: Sean Clifford finds Daniel George, who beats his defender with a sweet double move for a 95-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Penn State's Clifford connects with George for 95-yard TD
